title: Fully Customizable Password List
description:
Steps on creating your own customized PassList

1. Click the Button to the right and download the PassList 

2. COPY the ones that you want in one folder ONLY .TEXT FILES AND NOT THE HOLE FOLDER and rename him to your liking

3. Drag the creator programm in that folder and run it 

4. You now should have a yourPassList.txt file in your folder

5. Delete all the old .txt files in that folder NOT THE ONE FROM THE TORRENT

6. Now drag your personal PassList to any programm you want

( 7. rename your newly created list with the name of your target : MyOldLazyGrandpa.txt so you know what goes where )

8. KEEP BREATHING
